---
title: Easy Garlic-Herb Salmon & Basil Pesto Risoni Salad with Parmesan
description: Fresh and herby are meeting half way in a salad that’s going to bring peace to your craving for salmon and risoni. Salmon is
seasoned in herby garlic spices and the risoni is stirred through with soft basil pesto. As a peace offering that will seal the deal,
sprinkle over some Parmesan cheese.
